@@TJvXPCustomToolButton
Summary
  Base class for buttons that are drawn like the border icon buttons (minimize, maximize etc) in XP
  style.
Description
  Derive a new class from TJvXPCustomToolButton when you need to create a button control that is drawn
  like XP style border icon buttons. Don't create instances of TJvXPCustomToolButton. Instead use a
  derived class like TJvXPToolButton that publishes the properties and events of
  TJvXPCustomToolButton.

